title: ZBT Probes Alien Expert - ZBT #375

FIND ZBT: https://linktr.ee/ZeroBlog30 Five Rounds In The Magazine: Round 1: A down on his luck Air Force veteran got his vaccine shot & got more than a boost to his immunity Round 2: Our friends in New Zealand pulled off an insane rescue of an American in Antarctica Round 3: Secretary Austin talked about the future of artificial intelligence in the military and it’s absolutely wild. Round 5: A British Airman crashed through a roof in California!
